            <p style="font-size:12px">
                As an authorised representative of the Applicant, I/We acknowledge receipt of and accept on behalf of the Applicantthe term and conditions of sale and credit published or communicated to me by the Supplier <span style="font-weight: bold;">(Agreement)</span> (as amended from time to time). I/We further acknowledge and agree the Agreement will apply to the supply of any goods to the Applicant by the Supplier in precedence to any terms the Applicant may provide in any orders for any goods it places with the Supplier and warrant that I/We am/are authorised to sign this Credit Application and accept the Agreement on behalf of the Applicant and that the information given above is correct and that the Applicant is solvent and has never been insolvent or bankrupt. If the Applicant becomes insolvent in the opinion of the Suppliers, or breaches the Agreement, all amounts credited to the Applicant will become payable immediately. I/We undertake to advise the Supplier of any changes affecting the legal capacity, structure or management control of the Applicant and the Applicant’s Business.
